The evidence with the title 'EM9. Disposal of asbestos waste ' says This sheet describes good practice when you need to dispose of asbestos waste. Any asbestos product or material that is ready for disposal is defined as asbestos  ... Contaminated building materials, tools that cannot be decontaminated  ... More than 0.1 % asbestos.  ... Control of Asbestos Regulations 2012 and most waste. 
